<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>عَن صَالح أبي الْخَلِيل،<span class="c5"> وَهُوَ:</span> ابْن أبي مَرْيَم،<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وروى أَبُو الْيَد الطَّيَالِسِيّ، عَن زِيَاد ابْن عمر،<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>عَن صَالح أبي الْخَلِيل،<span class="c5"> وَهُوَ:</span> ابْن مُسلم.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>٢٥٧٦ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو الْخَلِيل:</span> بدر بن الْخَلِيل،<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>كُوفِي.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> مُجَاهِد.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> عِيسَى بن يُونُس وكناه.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>٢٥٧٧ - أَبُو الْخَلِيل.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">عَن:</span> ابْن عَبَّاس.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> سُلَيْمَان الْأَعْمَش.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>٢٥٧٨ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو الْخَلِيل:</span> اسْمه: بزيع.<span class="c5"> حدث عَن:</span> الْأَعْمَش.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>٢٥٧٩ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو الْخَلِيل:</span> عبد السَّلَام بن عجلَان،<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c5">وَقيل:</span> ابْن غَالب، بَصرِي.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> سعيد بن جُبَير.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> أَبُو سَلمَة مُوسَى بن إِسْمَاعِيل<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>وَغَيره <span class="c2">(ق ١٠٨ / ب)</span> .<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>٢٥٨٠ - أَبُو الْخَلِيل.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> سُلَيْمَان مُرْسل.<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> برذعة بن عبد الرَّحْمَن.<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>٢٥٨١ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو الْخَلِيل:</span> عتاب بن الْخَلِيل.<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span><span class="c2">(وَمن كنيته أَبُو خَيْثَمَة)</span><a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>٢٥٨٢ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو خَيْثَمَة:</span> عبد الرَّحْمَن بن أبي<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p23"></span>سُبْرَة.<a href="#p23" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p24"></span>لَهُ ذكر فِي الصَّحَابَة.<a href="#p24" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p25"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> ابْنه خَيْثَمَة بن عبد الرَّحْمَن.<a href="#p25" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p26"></span>أخبرنَا أَحْمد بن مهْرَان الْفَارِسِي، ثَنَا مُوسَى،<a href="#p26" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p27"></span>ثَنَا شباب،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> وَعبد الرَّحْمَن بن أبي<a href="#p27" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p28"></span>سُبْرَة أَبُو خَيْثَمَة.<a href="#p28" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p29"></span>٢٥٨٣ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو خَيْثَمَة:</span> عبد الله بن خَيْثَمَة<a href="#p29" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p30"></span>السالمي الخزرجي.<a href="#p30" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p31"></span>لَهُ صُحْبَة.<a href="#p31" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p32"></span>قَالَه مُحَمَّد بن عمر الْوَاقِدِيّ.<a href="#p32" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p33"></span>أخبرنَا مُحَمَّد بن أَحْمد بن إِسْحَاق الْمَدِينِيّ،<a href="#p33" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p34"></span>ثَنَا الْحسن بن الجهم، ثَنَا الْحُسَيْن بن الْفرج<a href="#p34" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p35"></span>عَنهُ.<a href="#p35" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p36"></span>٢٥٨٤ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو خَيْثَمَة:</span> سُلَيْمَان بن حَيَّان<a href="#p36" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p37"></span>الدِّمَشْقِي.<a href="#p37" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p38"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> وَاثِلَة.<a href="#p38" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p39"></span>قَالَه البُخَارِيّ.<a href="#p39" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p40"></span>٢٥٨٥ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو خَيْثَمَة:</span> زُهَيْر بن مُعَاوِيَة بن<a href="#p40" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p41"></span>حديج بن رحيل الْجعْفِيّ.<a href="#p41" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p42"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> أبي إِسْحَاق، وَأبي الزبير.<a href="#p42" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>